WEBVTT

00:00:06.342 --> 00:00:09.363
If you've watched the news
or followed politics

00:00:09.363 --> 00:00:11.839
chances are you've heard 
the term Orwellian

00:00:11.839 --> 00:00:14.834
thrown around 
in one context or another.

00:00:14.834 --> 00:00:17.821
But have you ever stopped to think
about what it really means,

00:00:17.821 --> 00:00:20.425
or why it's used so often?

00:00:20.425 --> 00:00:23.475
The term was named 
after British author Eric Blair

00:00:23.475 --> 00:00:26.883
known by his pen name George Orwell.

